channel.title: [Delta] How do I change where I log in? [Delta]
channel.description:
Okay, I had a super giga-omega brain fart.
I forgot how to change the place where I log in on a Delta server..
I have used the search tab so if you're going to post a comment saying anything regarding the search tab, please dont.
Anyway, I just recently restarted a server on a blank Delta base, and its home is at the Falador Park, and I need that to change.
I have my coordinates for my new home that I want (3093,3244) but I need to know where to exchange the Falador Park with this.
Also, on a Delta server, when you click 'home' it brings you to a random location in a square area, and I need to know how to change all of them
So if anyone could tell me the code and [b]where to put it[/b], that'd be great :D
Thanks!
~ Me ~
